name: Fine Art, Coastal Hampton style. Sugarloaf rock in Cape Naturaliste, Dunsborough, Western Australia
description:
This is a photo taken by me, a photographer living in Perth Western Australia.
This has been the best photograph I have ever taken since starting my photographic journey.
Weeks of preparation and getting up early untill finally pressing the shutter.
Capturing the famous Sugarloaf rock in all its glory on a sombre day with turbulent winds reflected in the cascading of water from the secondary rocks.
A beautiful piece of artwork that can be printed and would look beautiful in a coastal hamptons style house, or as a high res desktop background.
2048 x 1102px
Photographed with a Sony A7 mk I
with the Sigma 35 Art series lens @ 35mm

Limited to 15 editions, without any re releases.
